d\nreliable, it must be supported by a wide range of lens inversion methods.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 28 Jun 2018 18:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 8 Nov 2018 19:00:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-28"}
