ion and spin-up of comet\nnuclei, providing strong observational evidence for sublimation-driven\nrotational changes in comets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 28 Jun 2018 19:43:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-29"}
