nce to the detailed study of topological phonon\nphases in electronic materials, and the possibility of these phases to\nintroduce novel and more efficient use of thermoelectric materials in many\neveryday technological applications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 29 Jun 2018 13:31:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 2 Jul 2018 12:01:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-21"}
